text:
Yeah, it looks great on you.
It looks like it fits perfectly as well.

It was just about to not fit perfectly anymore
thanks to a certain someone...

Ah, sorry...
But just one snack surely won't matter....

Haa...
You'll really say something like that?

In the off chance that the waist is too tight or something,
wouldn't that be embarrasing?

If you aren't concerned about details like that,
It'll totally be a pain for me...

I-I see what you mean...
I'll be more careful in the future.

Snacks should be food that won't pile up in calories,
and you also have to be careful not to drink to much either...

As I thought, Producer is so serious.
Obviously, this was all just a joke.
